%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Pipeline
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as KubeRay Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Browser as User Browser

    Note over User, Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated CR (adds secure-trusted-network annotation)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created

    Note over Operator, Workers: Operator Reconciliation

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster events<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + Services<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Operator, CertMgr: Flow 4: mTLS Certificate Provisioning

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create cert-manager Issuer<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Certificate CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    CertMgr->>K8sAPI: Create TLS Secrets<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Operator, Gateway: Authentication Controller Setup

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute (/ray/{ns}/{cluster})<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicies<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>into Head Pod spec

    Note over Browser, HeadPod: Flow 2: Ray Dashboard Access (RHOAI 3.x)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/*<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>HeadPod: Forward to head-svc:8265<br/>HTTP plaintext (URL rewrite strips prefix)
    HeadPod-->>Gateway: Dashboard response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS response

    Note over Operator, HeadPod: Flow 3: RayJob Submission (K8sJobMode)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create submitter K8s Job<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job created
    Note right of HeadPod: Submitter pod connects to<br/>head-svc:8265 for job submission
    Operator->>HeadPod: Poll job status<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP plaintext
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Job status response
